TI  - Emerging implications of policies on malaria treatment: genetic changes in
      the Pfmdr-1 gene affecting susceptibility to artemether-lumefantrine and
      artesunate-amodiaquine in Africa
T2  - BMJ Glob. Health
JF  - BMJ global health
VL  - 3
IS  - 5
