TI  - High prevalence of sulphadoxine-pyrimethamine resistance-associated
      mutations in Plasmodium falciparum field isolates from pregnant women in
      Brazzaville, Republic of Congo
T2  - Infect. Genet. Evol.
JF  - Infection, genetics and evolution: journal of molecular epidemiology and evolutionary genetics in infectious diseases
VL  - 33
