TI  - The clinical impact of artemisinin resistance in Southeast Asia and the
      potential for future spread
T2  - FEMS Microbiol. Rev.
JF  - FEMS microbiology reviews
VL  - 41
IS  - 1
SP  - 34-48
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/9/8
