TI  - [Analysis of chloroquine-resistant gene polymorphisms in Plasmodium
      falciparum imported into China in 2012 and 2018]
T2  - Zhongguo Xue Xi Chong Bing Fang Zhi Za Zhi
JF  - Zhongguo xue xi chong bing fang zhi za zhi [Chinese journal of schistosomiasis control]
VL  - 32
