TI  - Molecular surveillance of anti-malarial drug resistance in Democratic
      Republic of Congo: high variability of chloroquinoresistance and lack of
      amodiaquinoresistance
T2  - Malar. J.
JF  - Malaria journal
VL  - 19
IS  - 1
SP  - 121
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/3/20
