TI  - Assessment of the Feasibility, Acceptability, and Impact of Implementing
      Seasonal Malaria Chemoprevention in Nampula Province, Mozambique: Protocol
      for a Hybrid Effectiveness-Implementation Study
T2  - JMIR Res. Protoc.
