TI  - Molecular and entomological surveillance of malaria vectors in urban and
      rural communities of Benguela Province, Angola
T2  - Parasit. Vectors
JF  - Parasites & vectors
VL  - 17
IS  - 1
SP  - 112
PY  - 2024
