TI  - Experimentally Engineered Mutations in a Ubiquitin Hydrolase, UBP-1,
      Modulate In Vivo Susceptibility to Artemisinin and Chloroquine in
      Plasmodium berghei
T2  - Antimicrob. Agents Chemother.
