TI  - Molecular determinants of sulfadoxine-pyrimethamine resistance in
      Plasmodium falciparum in Nigeria and the regional emergence of dhps 431V
T2  - Int. J. Parasitol. Drugs Drug Resist.
JF  - International journal for parasitology, drugs and drug resistance
