TI  - Detection of drug-resistant malaria in resource-limited settings:
      efficient and high-throughput surveillance of artemisinin and partner drug
      resistance
T2  - J. Antimicrob. Chemother.
JF  - The journal of antimicrobial chemotherapy
VL  - 79
IS  - 6
SP  - 1418-1422
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/6/3
