TI  - Characterization of pfmdr1, pfcrt, pfK13, pfubp1, and pfap2mu in Travelers
      Returning from Africa with Plasmodium falciparum Infections Reported in
      China from 2014 to 2018
T2  - Antimicrob. Agents Chemother.
JF  - Antimicrobial agents and chemotherapy
VL  - 65
IS  - 7
SP  - e0271720
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/6/17
