TI  - Prevalence of molecular markers of chloroquine resistance in malaria
      parasites in East Africa: A systematic review and meta-analysis
T2  - J. Glob. Antimicrob. Resist.
JF  - Journal of global antimicrobial resistance
VL  - 41
SP  - 117-137
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/12/25
