TI  - High prevalence of Pfcrt 76T and Pfmdr1 N86 genotypes in malaria infected
      patients attending health facilities in East Shewa zone, Oromia Regional
      State, Ethiopia
T2  - Malar. J.
JF  - Malaria journal
VL  - 21
IS  - 1
SP  - 286
PY  - 2022
