TI  - Molecular Epidemiology of Drug Resistance Genes in Plasmodium falciparum
      Isolates Imported from Nigeria between 2016 and 2020: Continued Emergence
      of Fully Resistant Pfdhfr-Pfdhps Alleles
T2  - Microbiol. Spectr.
