TI  - The prevalence of molecular markers of resistance to
      sulfadoxine-pyrimethamine among pregnant women at first antenatal clinic
      attendance and delivery in the forest-savannah area of Ghana
T2  - PLoS One
JF  - PloS one
VL  - 17
IS  - 8
