TI  - Examining the Early Distribution of the Artemisinin-Resistant Plasmodium
      falciparum kelch13 R561H Mutation in Areas of Higher Transmission in
      Rwanda
T2  - Open Forum Infect. Dis.
JF  - Open forum infectious diseases
