TI  - Seasonal Malaria Chemoprevention Implementation: Effect on Malaria
      Incidence and Immunity in a Context of Expansion of P. falciparum
      Resistant Genotypes with Potential Reduction of the Effectiveness in
      Sub-Saharan Africa
